OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783959568
OL,3,CWoman dies in house fire in
OL,4,CWarwickshire
OL,6,FA woman has died after a house fire in
OL,7,FWarwickshire.
OL,9,FFirefighters were called to the first-
OL,10,Ffloor maisonette in Marston Lane, in
OL,11,FBedworth, just before 6.30am on
OL,12,FSaturday, July 11.
OL,14,FCrews found a fire had broken out in
OL,15,Fthe kitchen and tackled it using hose
OL,16,Freel jets.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
