OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783959568
OL,3,CWoman dies in house fire in
OL,4,CWarwickshire
OL,6,FParamedics were also dispatched to the
OL,7,Fscene and found a woman with serious
OL,8,Finjuries. Nothing could be done to
OL,9,Fsave the woman and she was pronounced
OL,10,Fdead.
OL,12,FAnother woman was treated for smoke
OL,13,Finhalation and taken to George Eliot
OL,14,FHospital.
OL,16,FCones were placed near the affected
OL,17,Fproperty in Marston Lane while the
OL,18,Fcircumstances of the fire were
OL,19,Fexamined.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
