PN,34603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783959568
OL,3,CWoman dies in house fire in
OL,4,CWarwickshire
OL,6,FA spokesman for West Midlands
OL,7,FAmbulance Service said: "We were
OL,8,Fcalled to a fire at a property on
OL,9,FMarston Lane in Bedworth at 6.25am on
OL,10,FSaturday and sent three ambulances,
OL,11,Ftwo paramedic officers, and the
OL,12,FWarwickshire and Northamptonshire
OL,13,FCritical Care Car to the scene.
OL,15,F"Crews found a woman in a critical
OL,16,Fcondition and immediately began
OL,17,Fadministering advanced life support.
OL,18,FSadly, despite best efforts, nothing
OL,19,Fcould be done to save her, and she was
OL,20,Fconfirmed dead at the scene.
OL,26,@oD@YOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
