OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783959568
OL,3,CWoman dies in house fire in
OL,4,CWarwickshire
OL,6,F"A second woman was treated for the
OL,7,Fpossible effects of smoke inhalation
OL,8,Fand conveyed to George Eliot Hospital."
OL,10,FWarwickshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,11,Fsaid: "We were called at around 6.20am
OL,12,Fto reports of a fire at a property on
OL,13,FMarston Lane in Bedworth. Crews
OL,14,Fdiscovered a kitchen fire in a first-
OL,15,Ffloor maisonette.
OL,17,F"Crews tackled the fire using hose
OL,18,Freel jets and breathing apparatus.
OL,19,FWFRS had two appliances on scene and
OL,20,Fwere assisted by two crews from West
OL,21,FMidlands Fire Service.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@gO]sD@GOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
